parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: False Activation of Automatic Emergency Braking System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The false activation of the automatic emergency braking system can cause sudden and unexpected braking, leading to accidents, near-misses, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes without warning
even when there is no apparent obstacle or danger ahead. The braking system may beep or flash a warning light
and the vehicle may come to a complete stop or slow down rapidly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure of Collision Mitigation Braking System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the collision mitigation braking system can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, as the vehicle may not respond to potential hazards or obstacles on the road.
symptoms: The collision mitigation braking system warning light may appear on the dashboard
and the system may not function properly
failing to detect obstacles or brake in emergency situations.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Issues with Adaptive Cruise Control and Lane Departure System
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the adaptive cruise control and lane departure system can cause the vehicle to brake or accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The adaptive cruise control system may not function properly
causing the vehicle to brake or accelerate unexpectedly
or the lane departure system may fail to detect lane markings or obstacles.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Braking and Automatic Emergency Braking Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended braking and automatic emergency braking failure can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities. The sudden and unexpected braking can lead to rear-end collisions, loss of control, and other hazardous situations.
symptoms: The vehicle brakes suddenly and unexpectedly
often without any warning or obstacle detection. The brake light may illuminate
and the vehicle may come to a sudden stop or slow down rapidly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive wear and failure of rear brakes can lead to reduced stopping power, increased stopping distances, and accidents. The worn-out brake pads and rotors can also cause damage to other brake components, leading to costly repairs.
symptoms: The rear brake pads wear out prematurely
often at a rate disproportionate to the front brakes. The rotors may also show signs of excessive wear
such as rust or scoring.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake System Error Codes and False Warnings
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake system error codes and false warnings can distract the driver, cause confusion, and lead to accidents. The failure to diagnose and repair the underlying issues can result in continued problems and safety risks.
symptoms: The brake system warning lights illuminate
and error codes are displayed on the dashboard. The warnings may be false or misleading
and the underlying issues may not be properly diagnosed or repaired.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The brake pedal and booster issues can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities. The failure to repair or replace the faulty components can result in continued safety risks.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
or it may travel to the floor without resistance. The brake booster may malfunction
causing the brakes to fail or malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and safety risks, especially in hot weather conditions.
symptoms: AC not working
hissing noise
vibration in the seats.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the door lock actuator can cause safety risks, as doors may not lock or unlock properly, leaving the vehicle and occupants vulnerable.
symptoms: Intermittent or permanent failure of door lock actuators
doors unlocking or not locking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the fuel pump can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or strandings.
symptoms: Loud noise from the fuel pump
loss of power
stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The humming or whining noise can be distracting and annoying, causing discomfort and affecting the overall driving experience.
symptoms: Loud humming or whining noise

noise cancellation issues.
